OL,3,CCars: What's Driving The Costs?
OL,5,FThe average cost of running a car is
OL,6,Fnow thought to be around #3500 per
OL,7,Fyear, but what's causing costs to
OL,8,Frise? In Cars: What's Driving up
OL,9,FCosts? Tonight investigates how rising
OL,10,Fcosts are affecting motorists.
OL,12,F"Insurance costs have gone up
OL,13,Fmassively, and fuel costs, both for
OL,14,Fpetrol and diesel and electric cars
OL,15,Fare all going up as well, so there's
OL,16,Freally nowhere to hide when it comes
OL,17,Fto the day to day running costs with
OL,18,Fcars." - Michael Passingham, Which?
OL,26,@tD@AOUzD@FO]
