OL,3,CCars: What's Driving The Costs?
OL,5,FMotor repair costs are also on the up.
OL,6,FA survey by the Motor Ombudsman has
OL,7,Ffound more than two thirds of garages
OL,8,Fand workshops expect drivers to skip
OL,9,Fdoing vital work on their vehicles
OL,10,Fthis year as a quick way to save
OL,11,Fmoney. Azhar Mahmood who owns Napoleon
OL,12,FGarage in Bradford says it's a
OL,13,Fdifficult time for the industry,
OL,14,Fbecause of a combination of rising
OL,15,Fcosts and issues in the supply chain
OL,16,Ffor parts.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
