CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1772737887
OL,3,CCars: What's Driving The Costs?
OL,5,F"Costs are just climbing and climbing
OL,6,Fand climbing. Parts have started to
OL,7,Fbecome harder to obtain. Year on year.
OL,8,FThe challenges are becoming harder,
OL,9,Fthe struggles are harder." - Azhar
OL,10,FMahmood, Garage Owner
