OL,3,CCars: What's Driving The Costs?
OL,5,FDrivers are also facing issues before
OL,6,Fthey have even passed their tests. The
OL,7,Faverage wait time for a practical
OL,8,Fdriving test in the UK is nearly 22
OL,9,Fweeks, meaning learners are having to
OL,10,Fpay for extra lessons to keep their
OL,11,Fskills up to date. The DVSA says it
OL,12,Fhas already taken steps with the aim
OL,13,Fto get the wait down to an average of
OL,14,F7 weeks, but doesn't expect to achieve
OL,15,Fthis until November 2027. Ivy has been
OL,16,Ftaking lessons for over a year, and
OL,17,Fhas been waiting 6 months for her
OL,18,Fdriving test which is booked for later
OL,19,Fthis month.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
