OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1772737887
OL,3,CCars: What's Driving The Costs?
OL,5,F"A lot of times I'd go on the website
OL,6,Fand there wouldn't be any available. I
OL,7,Fhad quite an extended period of time
OL,8,Fwhere I didn't have a test booked and
OL,9,Fit was just difficult."
OL,11,F- Ivy, Learner Driver
OL,13,FThe average list price of new petrol
OL,14,Fcars has now reached #48,000, while
OL,15,Fthe average used car price is #17,000.
OL,16,FThat has made owning a car financially
OL,17,Fdifficult for some. Sarah has been
OL,18,Fusing a car club which offers short
OL,19,Fterm rentals of shared vehicles which
OL,20,Fcost from #5.50 an hour.
