OL,3,CCars: What's Driving The Costs?
OL,5,FEVs have historically been more
OL,6,Fexpensive to buy, but that gap is
OL,7,Fgradually closing. The government
OL,8,Fplans to introduce a pay per mile EV
OL,9,Ftax in two year's time. But it's still
OL,10,Foffering incentives to buyers, with
OL,11,Fmany new models eligible for discounts
OL,12,Fthrough the electric car grant. Jackie
OL,13,Ffrom County Durham made the switch to
OL,14,FEV through a workplace salary
OL,15,Fsacrifice scheme, but misses out on
OL,16,Fcheaper charging because she can't
OL,17,Fcharge her car at home.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
