CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1772737887
OL,3,CCars: What's Driving The Costs?
OL,5,F"I'm consistently paying 20% VAT on
OL,6,Fthe electricity that I charge my car
OL,7,Fwith, where people who can charge at
OL,8,Fhome are only paying 5% VAT on the
OL,9,Felectricity that they're using for
OL,10,Ftheir cars."
OL,12,F- Jackie, EV Owner
